node.text:
Hafsah 💕 Farewell 1/6

Hello!!! It’s been forever since I’ve posted because university decided to tie me to a train track and drive a train over me 😊 But it’s okay, I have made it out (albeit with a lot of deep, deep scars.) I finally got done with my finals which means I can take and post photos! Starting off with this farewell shoot of the sweetest girls 🥺

.
.
Here’s the last of the photos for now! Might post more from the other events later, let’s see :) Thank you so much for all the love you’ve shown these photos 💛 Crying, brb.

.

There’s a couple more I want to post but right now does not feel like the time. Throwback karein ge kisi din 😋
